<BaseLayout title="Legacy IT Consulting – The IT Guys" description="Information about The IT Guys' legacy IT consulting services for businesses in the Kelowna, British Columbia area.">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">Legacy IT Consulting</p>
    <h1>Trusted IT support remains part of our story.</h1>
    <p class="lede">The IT Guys – Technical Solutions Inc. has provided professional IT consulting and technical support for small and medium-sized businesses in the Kelowna region since 2018.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="section split">
    <div>
      <h2>Selective consulting, built on long-term trust.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="copy">
      <p>Our primary focus today is software and mobile application development. However, our history in IT consulting continues to shape how we approach every technical problem.</p>
      <p>We continue to support select consulting clients where the relationship, fit, and scope make sense.</p>
      <ul class="list">
        <li>Small business IT guidance</li>
        <li>Technology planning and troubleshooting</li>
        <li>Systems, security, and workflow consultation</li>
        <li>Support for existing long-term clients</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
